<A>__{the myopic janitor looks down. five floors below a man lays on his back. his shotgun discharges uselessly into trees. another man leans over him. illuminates his agonized face with a flash light. shoots him again point blank in the upper body. the myo pic isn't staying for more. hurries back along the fire escape.}
